channel.title: Server status page ! Server offline? Need help please!
channel.description:
I know many people have the same question I do.
When I try to post my server on the moparscape Server status page it says
"The server 0wnage server!! is offline, it must be online before you can register it"
I have a no-ip, no-ip duc, im portforwarded, and my server is running. So why can't i post my server??
PLease help!!! :confused:
